description:
ACK is an action/sci-fi/humor comic about a 14-year old who comes into possession of a mysterious cube capable of transforming into a powerful (and wearable) robot arm. Soon, the kid finds out there are other cubes out there, each unlocking a different robot part, and someone is looking for them... ACK is inspired by Mega Man X, DBZ, Saint Seiya, Robotech and everything awesome, with some oddball humor thrown into the blender for good measure.

This torrent contains the full first chapter of ACK (32 pages) in CBR format. You can download it in other formats and languages at the official site: http://www.ackwebcomic.com/ Chapter 2 is coming in March 2014!

